{"about_the_game":"A lot of options. You can build up tiles with different buildings, go to the production of wheat, wood, stone or faith. Or create a balanced option. One option will be good for later abdication and getting gold, the other for hero leveling, the third, for example, for a quick restart, and so on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can choose the pantheon (from several options - in a sense, how the pantheon is selected in Civilization 5), and then choose religion and god. Each pantheon has its own effect, and each god has 3 perks, and every perk has its own effect also. In addition, for the gods, you can choose religious servants. There is a lot of combinations.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can build an academy and hire a hero. Hero fights for tiles. You can choose a hero class. And before each fight, you can choose a weapon, shield and helmet. Again, many options.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game gradually opens new content, new strategies of the game appear from it.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd since idle games involve restarts, you can restart for profit and at the same time try a different combination and strategy.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Get Tiles I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1017100/c4db23e423080783a149cff2b17132136edd3a84.jpg"},{"name":"Get Tiles II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1017100/1262bf2dd3aacdc63f76fbba11e803a0a5c77aca.jpg"},{"name":"Get Tiles III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1017100/99e04e80fadb4c9d62a4cb38a08aa5fec47fd127.jpg"},{"name":"Get Tiles IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1017100/d472a096327faa61a5578959c5e5baa876fc4f0a.jpg"},{"name":"Get Tiles V","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1017100/80c69c02b78a8c3654d2437ff1d2ce60e3793061.jpg"},{"name":"Buy Tiles I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/stea